Dialogs.Dialog: When you see this water fountain, are you reminded of the time before we started dating？
姉ヶ崎
Yeah. Before I went to work for the part-time job, I often ran into you here.
Actually, you went out of your way to come here, didn't you？
Yeah... But it was because I really liked this place.
Plus, I was thinking that I might be able to meet you here.
So, that was what you were thinking since back then, huh？
Geez... Isn't it obvious？ Don't ask. It's embarrassing.
Ah, a cat.
姉ヶ崎
So cute~
Ah, I don't have anything to feed you. Um... Ah, I have this cough drop.
You wanna eat this cough drop？ Come here, come here.
Meow, meow~
A-Ah... It's gone.
...I wonder if cats will eat cough drops.
Urgh~
姉ヶ崎
Hey, when we walk together like this, what do people see us as？
What do you mean？
Do they see us as a girlfriend and a boyfriend, or an older sister and her brother？
We are lovers, right？
Eh？ Ah, yeah...
So, just that fact is enough, isn't it？
...Yeah, you're right. Sorry for saying something strange.
姉ヶ崎
Speaking of which, there are many shrines that have long stairs.
Is that so？
Yeah, this shrine, too... Are they like stairways to heaven？
It's a shrine, after all.
When you're walking by my side, every place turns into heaven for me.
(This is embarrassing...)
By the way, do you know what this shrine was built for？ To worship a specific God？
姉ヶ崎
Hmm, speaking of which, I don't really know much, but I think it enshrines the God of Marriage.
Really？
So... Hey...
...Don't tell me you've already made your wish here.
Hehe. That's my secret~
姉ヶ崎
I really love the scenery when I look from here.
The overview of our city, huh？
Our city hasn't changed much. But it seems to have changed when I look at the city from here.
Hmm... It's such a nice, peaceful city.
Isn't it？ Ah, look over there. Over there...
姉ヶ崎
Ah, it was interesting. Just perfect.
Yeah, I didn't expect that it'd be this good.
Hehe. If you expected too much, you'd be shocked if it turned out to be bad, right？
Yeah, but this one is going to be a big hit, I think.
Yeah, a big hit. A real big one.
How was it？
姉ヶ崎
Hm, it was just so-so. Ah, I have to buy a pamphlet. Can you wait here？
It was so-so but you'll still buy a pamphlet？
I buy pamphlets for any movie I watch. Even for very boring movies.
You buy pamphlets for boring movies too？
They are so boring that they become interesting for me.
So boring that they become interesting...？
姉ヶ崎
Urgh...
Um... You hated it that much？
Yeah. Bad actors, bad pictures, bad music, and bad scenario. It was the worst.
R-Really...？
Ah... Sorry. It wasn't to my tastes, so I... This side of me really isn't good, right？
姉ヶ崎
Hehe. How about we have a match？
No problem, but... ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲, are you good at bowling？
Nope, not at all.
Yet you want a match？
I know my gentle boyfriend will at least give me some handicaps.
Indeed. Then I'll let ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲ have twice the scores.
Hehe. Take it seriously, okay？ I really want to see how cool you can be.
Ah, it's a 5-10 split... This is gonna be tough.
姉ヶ崎
Hehe. If you can get them down, I'll give you a reward.
All right！
Wow, amazing... You really got them all. Now, as I promised...
That's it？
Hehe. Not enough？
(Hmm, that's fine though.)
姉ヶ崎
Ah, it went out again... What can I do to bowl straight？
Isn't it rather amazing that you could make a curve like that？
But it went down the gutter. It's a gutter ball. Boo boo.
...But it could be the hidden talent that you've never found out, right？
The second round starts now.
姉ヶ崎
It's been a while since I felt this content.
Yeah. It was really great.
Did it hit you？ It's much better to feel it throughout your body, instead of just watching and listening.
Shall we come back again？
Hehe. If you ask me out, okay？
Hah... I was so pumped up that I'm getting tired now.
姉ヶ崎
Haha, I haven't had this kind of thrill in quite a while. Did it make you shudder？
▲姉ヶ崎＊▲, you enjoyed it, right？
Sort of... But, my heart was throbbing because you were near me...
Ah... No. Forget what I just said！ Ah... Geez...
姉ヶ崎
Um... Hey, did you... like it？
Well... Did you hate it？
I didn't hate it, but... Well, I just didn't really like it.
I see...
Ah, no. Today was fun. But, maybe... You know...
姉ヶ崎
Hey, hey. Let's sing this song next.
This is the song from an old superhero series. ...You wanna sing it？
Of course. Ah... Don't tell me you don't know this song.
No way. Let's sing together.
Okay. Since we're already at the karaoke, let's sing it out loud.
姉ヶ崎
Ah, I know this song.
▲姉ヶ崎＊▲, I chose this for you. Here's the microphone.
Eh！？ But this is a very cheesy love song！！？
That's why I want to hear you sing it. Come on.
Ah, geez... This is embarrassing...
姉ヶ崎
Okay, I entered a song for you. You sing it, okay？
Me？
Yeah, it's my favorite song.
I see... Okay. For ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲'s sake, I'll sing with all my heart.
Ah... Somehow, I'm the one who feels embarrassed now.
姉ヶ崎
Wow...
This is amazing... We can see faraway places clearly from here.
It's even higher than the high ground of the shrine. Look.
This is our city, huh...？
Yeah... Thank you for coming to live in this city.
姉ヶ崎
Hey, look. When we are at the top, don't you feel like our car is the only one in the air？
When you say so... This feels quite amazing.
People in the other cars won't be able to see us here, right？
Yeah, I don't think they can see us.
Hehe. Don't do anything perverted to me, okay？
I-I won't.
You won't？
Well...
Hehe. This part of you is very cute...
姉ヶ崎
Hey... I wish this haunted house would be better than this.
It's not scary for you？
Hehe, if I get scared by stuff like this, I can't be a horror movie fan, right？
Kyaa...！
...You're not scared, right？
I-I was just surprised. Yeah, that was a surprise.
姉ヶ崎
Kyaa！ It's scary.
You're not actually scared at all, aren't you？
No, I'm a little scared. That's why I want you to hold me like this.
That's my arm, you know？
Hehe, I've been longing for this.
Somehow, I understand this feeling.
If so, as my boyfriend, you should do what I want, okay？
姉ヶ崎
H-Hey...
W-What is it？
My hand... Won't you take my hand？
All right. ...Like this？
A-Ah... Thanks-- Kyaaaa！！
Whoaaaa！！
The first part when it's going up like this makes me feel nervous.
姉ヶ崎
Yeah, do you regret choosing this one？
Actually, a little.
Ahaha... Me, too.
Kyaaaa！
姉ヶ崎
Wow... Beautiful... This is like a dream...
What if this were actually a dream？ What would you do？
You mean the parade？
Everything. I would be just a part of your dream...
In that case... I wouldn't want to wake up, ever...
姉ヶ崎
When I was a kid, I used to try to imitate this.
The parade？ How？
I wrapped the Christmas tree's light bulbs all around myself. The sparkling light was so pretty.
That was dangerous. You shouldn't have tried that.
Yeah. I was scolded badly. So, don't ever try it, okay？
姉ヶ崎
When I was a kid, I dreamed about riding on that car.
Hmm？ When I get a driver's license, I'll buy that kind of car, then.
Will you hang light bulbs around it, too？
Yeah, I'll make it sparkling.
Like a commercial car？
Eh...？ Ah, I've seen a truck with some light bulbs like that.
Hehe. I think just a normal car would be fine. But you must reserve the passenger's seat for only me... okay？
Wow...
姉ヶ崎
Eh？ What？ What is it？
No... It's just that ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲ looks so nice in a swimsuit...
Hehe. Are you falling head over heels for me？
I'm already head over heels for you.
Geez... That's my line, you know？
姉ヶ崎
It's nice that people who can't swim can also have fun in a swimming pool.
Have you ever thought about learning how to swim？
Well, that's true...
Yeah, people live even if they don't know how to swim. So I'm good.
You don't have to take it that seriously...
姉ヶ崎
It's nice that we don't have to worry about getting sunburns at the indoor swimming pool.
That's not true. It has a skylight and we get some amount of sunlight here.
Eh？ Really？ I don't want the swimming suit's tanlines on my body.
Ah, that's right.
Hehe. Don't tell me you wanna see it.
Eh！？
Hey, don't take it seriously. Geez.
姉ヶ崎
Beautiful, isn't it...？
Yeah, we can't see something like this if we stay in the city.
I wonder if we can see them if we're on the mountain...
We'll go to see it someday. I want to see the real starry sky.
Yeah... I'll go with you.
姉ヶ崎
Say... Is it okay to hold hands？
No problem... But, why？
Hehe... This really feels like space and I feel like I'll get sucked in. ...Weird, huh？
Even if we were really in space, I wouldn't let go of your hand.
Yeah... Never let go.
姉ヶ崎
Hey...
What...？
So, you're here.
Yeah, I am.
I see...
I'm always at your side...
Yeah...
姉ヶ崎
Wow, so warm.
It's the subtropical plants corner... Isn't it a bit too hot？
Hehe. So it's summer in here all year round, huh？
If not, maybe these plants will wither, right？
It always feels like summer break in here.
It's like the summer break is locked up in this place... Hehe. This botanical garden is interesting.
姉ヶ崎
The air here feels good. Probably because there is more oxygen in here.
It smells different in here as well.
Ah, that's true... Nice smell... Which flower does this smell come from？
Hmm... I wonder which one.
Let's search for it.
Okay. Now then, let's check them one by one.
Hehe. We are like butterflies being lured by flowers' fragrances.
姉ヶ崎
It'd be nice if humans can do photosynthesis like plants.
Like plants？
In that case, we'll be okay with just light, water, and soil. Wouldn't that be peaceful？
But then our skin would be green.
Urgh... I don't like that. Hmm, humans are humans after all.
姉ヶ崎
Ah, it was fun.
Yeah, very satisfied. It was really great.
I want to come here again.
We'll come here together, okay？
Okay. Together... Hehe.
姉ヶ崎
I was planning to relax here, but I ended up being serious with it.
▲姉ヶ崎＊▲, too？
Now, I'm quite tired. Hey, can you carry me on your back？
That's a little...
Hey！ You are a man. This is shameful.
▲姉ヶ崎＊▲, what's wrong？
姉ヶ崎
Well... People really have different tastes, right？
You thought it was boring, then？
Yeah, very boring.
Is that so？ I'm sorry.
Hehe. Next time, take me somewhere fun, okay？
姉ヶ崎
Did you know？ If a couple holds hands and walks across this bridge, they will be blessed with happiness.
Really？
No.
Hehe. But what if it were real？
Of course, I'd walk across it together with ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲.
Then... How about we become the first couple to do this？ Hehe, it'll be nice, right？
姉ヶ崎
No matter how many times I look, it's always amazing...
You mean the bridge？
Yeah. Something as big as this can be built by humans.
What's wrong？
I'm fascinated by the look of ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲, when you're fascinated by the bridge.
Geez...
姉ヶ崎
Ah, it's too windy.
If the wind is this strong, maybe you can fly.
Hey, I'm not a little kid, so I wouldn't fly.
Ahaha, that's true.
I only used an umbrella as a parachute during a hurricane when I was a kid.
(Again, I didn't expect that...)
姉ヶ崎
The sun is very strong... Is this what people call the burning heat？
Yeah. You can get sunburnt if you stay like this for the whole day.
When I get sunburnt, the skin on the tip of my nose can be peeled off.
Eh？ I think that's kind of cute. I want to see it.
No. I'd look like a boy. That's embarrassing.
姉ヶ崎
...Hah.
What's wrong？ Why are you sighing all of a sudden？
No, I just got scared.
Scared of what？
But, to be able to come to the sea with you like this, I'm very happy, okay？
Would it be good if I wore sunglasses when I come here？
姉ヶ崎
The sun is very strong, huh？ But, for a high school student, wearing sunglasses would make you look like a delinquent.
▲姉ヶ崎＊▲ would look good with sunglasses.
Eh？ Really？ Wouldn't I look like a bad girl？
No, you're pretty, so I think you'd look more like a private idol.
Ah... Geez. Even if you praise me, I don't have anything for you.
There's no one here.
姉ヶ崎
But isn't it wonderful to have just the two of us here？ Let's stay like this for a while, okay？
...But we're gonna catch a cold.
Geez. I thought I could get you in the mood！
...But, it's very cold here. We'd better go home.
姉ヶ崎
In summer, people come here to swim, but now... there's nothing to do here.
Yeah. There aren't many people coming here...
Hehe. The off-season sea is such a secluded date spot.
Is that so？
Well... Since you're already here, how about you walk along the beach with this big sister？
When it's not summer, it's very cold at the sea.
姉ヶ崎
Really？ I don't think it's that cold. I even feel like swimming.
But you didn't bring a swimsuit...
Isn't it okay？ We didn't wear anything when we were born. It's just the two of us here.
...A-Are we gonna be naked？
Hehe. I'm just kidding. ...Your face is red. That's so cute. Geez.
This sunfish is huge...
姉ヶ崎
Because it lives in the ocean... doesn't it？
Does that matter？
Hmm, I don't really know, but... Let's see. Goldfish that live in a pond usually are big, right？
Hmm, is that so？
If we raised this sunfish in a bowl, it would be very small... I think. Hmm, I believe so. Yeah.
(I don't think it's true, though...)
姉ヶ崎
Do you feel sleepy when you watch the sunfish？
Are you getting sleepy？
No, but it's quite relaxing to watch these sunfish. If I keep watching, I will surely fall asleep.
Ah, I kind of understand that feeling.
Really...？ Instead of counting sheep when you can't sleep, counting sunfish might be better.
...Huh？
One sunfish... Two sunfish... Eh？ How many sunfish have I counted？
姉ヶ崎
Ah, penguins are so cute.
▲姉ヶ崎＊▲, do you like cute animals？
Have you seen girls who hate cute things？
I think you're right...
But, for you, the only girl you can like is me... What do you say about it？
For me, having you is more than enough.
Hehe. Then I'll love you much more for the sake of other girls too.
姉ヶ崎
When we look at the penguins like this, they sure are huge.
▲姉ヶ崎＊▲, did you imagine that they would be smaller？
Yeah, much smaller... Like, so small that it could stand on my palm.
A penguin that could stand on your palm？
Yeah, that would be cute. Hehe. Would they go flapping their wings while standing on my palms？
Flapping, flapping.
Ahaha. That's cute, ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲.
Eh？ Ah... Geez. Don't tease me.
姉ヶ崎
Wow~ Amazing！ This is beautiful...
It feels like we're really walking under the sea.
Yeah, it's like we are under the sea.
This is like another world...
No, there are a lot of things in this world that we haven't seen yet, you know？
Is that so...？ Yeah, that might be true.
Hehe, I'm really looking forward to it. The day when we both explore the world we've never known.
姉ヶ崎
This tunnel should be much much longer than this, huh？
Do you like it？
Yeah, I even want to live in here.
How about finding a job here in the future？
Working and living are totally different things. Ah... But they're the same for a housewife.
...Is that something you worry about？
姉ヶ崎
Ah, the dolphins are cute. I want to ride on them.
I think some other aquariums might allow you to ride them, but it's not allowed here.
Really？ Hey, will you take me to the other aquarium？
You wanna ride on them？ But ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲, you can't swim...
Boo boo.
Dolphins are as clever as dogs, right？ They're pretty smart.
姉ヶ崎
Yeah, but that depends. There are many breeds of dogs, and some are smarter than others, right？
Then... how smart are dolphins？
As smart as a dachshund？
Really？
I think a dachshund would be a nice match for a dolphin. Hehe. Shall we try to investigate this together？
(A nice match？ ...In what way？)
姉ヶ崎
Wow, nice view. Ah, we can see the Bay Bridge from here.
Hmm？ A boat is coming at the right moment. ...It looks a like a scene in a painting.
I used to dream of traveling alone on a big boat and spending a few months on it.
You "used to"？ A past tense？
Yeah, past tense. I don't dream of traveling alone anymore.
姉ヶ崎
We can smell salt water...
Yeah. We can feel the ocean breeze even from here.
I like the ocean. Although it's a bit scary at night, I still love it.
Right. I think ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲'s image matches the ocean nicely.
Really？ Hehe... Ah, I really want to ride a big boat someday...
Hmm, this feels good.
姉ヶ崎
Yeah, it feels so good that I'm getting sleepy.
At this hour！？
Hmm... I didn't sleep much last night.
...Ah, did it feel like the day before a trip, and you couldn't fall asleep？
Eh？ Ah... That wasn't the case...
姉ヶ崎
Wow. Such a beautiful view here.
This is nearly 50 meters high. It's like an observatory, but a little lower.
Um, I think it's high enough. This is very high up.
Ah, we can see the park on the other side of the coast, too. And that one over there is the stadium, I guess.
Huh？ You know a lot. Amazing, amazing.
Actually, I studied the info beforehand.
Ah, I see... Hehe. Good job, good job.
Do they sell thermometers as souvenirs here？
姉ヶ崎
Huh？ What？
Like a miniature tower that has a thermometer stuck on it.
Ah, I've seen them. There are different towers from all over the world.
I wonder if I can also find them here.
Hehe. It's our hometown's tower, so I'm not quite excited about it. ...But I'll help you look.
姉ヶ崎
Aha, we've finally arrived. Actually, I'm not very comfortable with an elevator, particularly when it's going down.
Huh？ Why？
Well, it feels like I'm going to be sucked down to the bottom of the earth...
If you were there, you could meet with underworld people.
Ah... Right. If I think about it that way, then I'm not scared.
姉ヶ崎
Ah, this is nice. Oh, that one is also cute. Hmm, I really can't choose.
You don't have to worry about me. Just take your time choosing.
Okay, thanks. Kyaa！ They have this thing too. This is nice.
This is what girls are like, huh？
Eh？ What？
No, I was talking to myself.
Sorry, I'm kind of worried about you-- Ah！ This thing was hidden here. It'll match that one perfectly.
I'm okay. I don't really care much about fashion.
姉ヶ崎
No good. This is the era where guys have to think about fashion, too.
But, well... It's a little...
Ah, that one might suit you well. Ah, this one is nice too. Why don't you try them on？
But, I said that I don't...
Hey, hurry up. Ah, this one is also nice. Come on. Just try them.
(She's forcing me...)
▲姉ヶ崎＊▲, I think you don't wear makeup.
姉ヶ崎
Usually, I don't. I just apply some facial moisturizer after bath.
How about your body？
Well, yeah. I apply some cream there too.
I see. It's quite troublesome to be a girl.
Hehe. We have to go through so many hardships that guys could never imagine.
姉ヶ崎
When I go to a party, maybe I need to apply some makeup.
Speaking of which, ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲, you don't use cosmetics, do you？
Hehe. Do you want to see how I look when I wear makeup？
Yeah. I want to see a lot more different sides of ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲.
I see... Well, I might have to think about it.
Accessories, huh...？ Maybe I should buy something, too.
姉ヶ崎
How about a bracelet？
A silver ring might be better. I don't want to be gaudy.
Silver accessories can be used as an amulet. Maybe I should buy one too.
How about matching rings？ Do you like them？
I do, I do. Yeah, I like them.
Hehe, I really do agree if you want to buy them.
▲姉ヶ崎＊▲, I think this will suit you nicely.
姉ヶ崎
Which one？ Ah, so cute... Um, but it's useless. They are pierces.
Ah, you don't have your ears pierced.
Right. Isn't it scary to have a hole in your ear？
But you're okay with horror movies.
That's different. But these are very cute. Hmm, now I'm regretting it.
It's so quiet that it's somehow scary.
姉ヶ崎
Yeah, but it's moving... It's the kind of stillness where it's actually moving gently.
Are we possibly disturbing it？
Ah... That's true. We must be quiet. Shhh~
Shhh~
姉ヶ崎
Ah, did you see it？ Did you see that？
Yeah, the jumping fish.
What was it...？ A salmon？
I can't really tell.
The store we just walked past sold grilled salmon. It must be a salmon.
(Don't jump to conclusions like that...)
▲姉ヶ崎＊▲, can you ride a bicycle？
姉ヶ崎
Eh？ I can, but... Do I look like someone who can't even ride a bicycle？
That's not the case. Look. There's a bicycle rental shop.
Ah... Hehe. I wonder if they also have tandems.
I doubt that. Let's take a look.
Okay.
姉ヶ崎
Aha, this feels nice. It's like I'm having a boat trip.
It would be swaying more than this in the ocean.
Really？
Yeah. How about we take a trip on a boat somewhere later？
Hehe. I was planning to do that on my honeymoon. So, we should wait... okay？
Ah, look. Those people on the camping ground are waving to us... Hello！
姉ヶ崎
No... Stop it.
Why？
Because... they are all girls...
Sorry. Well then... ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲, hello！
...Hehe. Hello~
姉ヶ崎
Ah, that bird is beautiful. What's it called？
Hmm... I only know doves, sparrows, and ostriches... Also chicken if you count them as birds.
Hehe. Penguins, too, right？
If we had a camera, we could take its picture and check later... A cell phone camera won't do, huh？
No, it's fine. Since it was pretty, I was just wondering what it was called. I'm having fun.
All right. Come on. ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲, are you okay？
姉ヶ崎
Yeah, I'm fine. Hah, you really are a man.
Come on. Give me your hand. All right.
Phew. Thanks. ...Sorry. I'm slow.
Don't worry. I'll also try to walk slower.
Fine. I'll do my best. All right, let's go.
姉ヶ崎
Wow, beautiful view.
Do you like it？
Yes！ Thanks for taking me up here.
You're welcome. Shall we rest for a bit？
Yeah. Actually, I'm quite exhausted. I'm glad you noticed.
When you have to walk for a long distance, it's better if you don't raise your knees too high while walking.
姉ヶ崎
Is that so？ Well, should I walk like this？
Yeah. Like you have only a small space between the ground and the soles of your feet.
Ah, really. This is a little more comfortable. Hehe.
Can you still walk a little longer？
Yeah, that's okay. But... Hehe... I kind of want us to hold hands. How's that？
姉ヶ崎
So beautiful. The whole mountain now looks like a sunset.
Such magnificent changes in colors...
At a time like this, I feel very lucky to be born as a Japanese.
We have cherry blossoms in the spring and maple leaves in the fall, huh...？
Hehe, you've become quite poetic. Is it because of the fall scenery？
姉ヶ崎
Are those maple leaves？ They are all red and so beautiful.
You're right. They are red and beautiful...
I feel like they will taste very good if we deep fry them.
I don't think that has anything to do with the colors though.
Hehe, I'm getting hungry just talking about this.
姉ヶ崎
It's great that the weather is so nice. The snow is quite dazzling.
As I thought. ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲ looks great in a ski suit.
Really？ Do I look like an idol who comes here for a private trip？
Yes, something like that.
Hey, if you don't stop flattering me like that, I'll bury you under the snow.
Then shall we take the lift？
姉ヶ崎
Ah, um...
Eh？ Are you afraid of high places？
No, I'm fine with high places, but I don't like to ride vehicles on high places.
I see. I'm sorry for not noticing that.
Don't worry. I won't get scared as long as you're with me. So... Can we hold hands？
姉ヶ崎
Hehe. I won.
Urgh... I lost... ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲, you're very good at this.
Hehe, my cousin taught me when I was in grade school.
Hmph. Your cousin？ He's a guy, right？
Hehe, are you jealous？
He's now a 40-something uncle and already married. ...Shall we go for another round？ Let's ski along side each other, okay？
...Hmm.
姉ヶ崎
Are you interested in it？
Nah, rather than interested... I don't even know what it is.
It's an abstract painting. So, it can be anything you think it is.
So, that's how to view it.
Hehe, take you time to look. I'll ask you later what you think about it.
Oh, look at that portrait. No matter where you are, it still looks like it's staring at you...
姉ヶ崎
It feels like those eyes are following us.
Yeah, that's right.
So, while we're looking at the portrait, the portrait is also looking at us.
That's... very profound.
姉ヶ崎
Somehow, I feel like painting something...
▲姉ヶ崎＊▲, do you paint？
